description.0: Carnage is unleashed in his First Appearance!  The spawn of Venom is the result of the criminally insane inmate Cletus Kasady bonding with a symbiote resulting in deadly creature of violence and insanity. Witness Spider-Man’s first battle against Carnage, ending in bloodshed!  The psychotic and brutal legacy of Carnage starts here and only Spider-Man and Venom can stop him.
description.1: Operation Galactic Storm Part 12. Deathbird sneaks her way into the Kree capital to assassinate their leaders...but when the Avengers attempt to stop her, the Kree misunderstand their intentions and declare the Avengers enemies of the empire.
description.2: After reaching the Kree Homeworld, Captain America along with his team of Avengers launch infiltration rescue mission to save Rick Jones. But when Iron Man discovers the Kree's master plan, the Avengers turn their sights on the Supremor!
description.3: OPERATION: GALACTIC STORM PART 9 In the midst of galactic war, U.S. Agent keeps ticking off his teammates. But before he can attend sensitivity training, the Shi'ar Imperial Guard attacks in a rescue mission all their own! Mockingbird makes a shocking discovery about Dr. Minerva's identity, but not before another Shi'ar starship escapes the Avengers' hold.
description.4: OPERATION: GALACTIC STORM PART 11 In the heart of the Nega-Portal, Wonder Man talks to Vision about his love for Wanda. Talk about bad timing. When the portal is revealed to be a bomb, Wonder Man and the Starjammers must fly for the hills and save their tails! Oh, and prevent a nuclear attack that would perpetaute an intergalactic war.
description.5: What if the Cosmic Avengers and Guardians of the Galaxy were defeated by Korvac? And how does this universe tie-in to the Time-Keepers plot to erase universes themselves?
description.6: OPERATION: GALACTIC STORM PART 10 Quasar vs. Neutron in one of the most pivotal battles of Galactic Storm! Binary pulls the wool over Wendell's eyes, leaving him vulnerable to yet another battle with the Shi'ar Imperial Guard. And boy, are they angry from that earlier defeat!
description.10: If anyone can survive Typhoid's kiss… it's Wolverine.
description.11: Wolverine and Nightcrawler are "bonded" in Winzeldorf when they come across a pack of monsters and an abandoned castle!
description.21: Doctor Strange and his team battle and soon defeat Nox and her sons, but could this easy victory be part of a bigger plan?
description.23: Daredevil’s “Nocturnal Hunter” is none other than the Owl! And this night-stalking foe has more power than ever before.
description.24: Destination: Ireland! Excalibur is drawn to the Emerald Isle to investigate an unusual force living deep within the Earth! Meanwhile back at their base, Widget has some new improvements of his own...
description.26: Iron Man rockets onward to Hala... in the face of Shatterrax! When Iron Man journeys to outer space with Captain America and the Avengers, Tony Stark finds himself in an Intergalactic conflict between Earth and the Kree!
description.27: Frank Castle's war on crime as the Punishers turns the Marvel Universe into a warzone! Who is Shotgun and can the Punisher really go undercover to take down a big target?
description.28: OPERATION: GALACTIC STORM PART 7 Thor takes up the hammer alongside Earth's Mightiest to defeat Gladiator of the Shi'ar Imperial Guard. The team, overpowered by Lilandra's right-hand man, banishes Gladiator to deep Shi'ar space. The only problem? The Avengers were transported to deep-space too, and now face an entire alien armada!
description.30: Wolfsbane finds herself in distress after she is mistaken as a member of the Pantheon. Kidnapped by religious zealots, will Rahne be able to escape with her life? X-Factor vs. the Pantheon! Guest-starring the Hulk!
description.31: The Human Torch gets roped into a game of cat and mouse by none other than the Amazing Spider-Man! Meanwhile, the rest of the FF takes on an interdimensional menace known as Wildblood!
description.32: Colossus' brother seems to be alive, but do his eyes deceive him?
description.33: While Wolverine, Mystique and Spiral travel to the end of time to fight Plasma Wraiths, Mojo enters the present and kidnaps Jubilee!
description.37: After Death's Head II absorbs 104 subjects, subject 105...a.k.a. the original Death's Head...comes a callin'.
description.38: The Living Eraser ruins Jen and Wyatt's date night!
description.42: OPERATION: GALACTIC STORM PART 2 Rick Jones is missing in hyperspace, or at least that's what the West Coast Avengers think! Rick Jones, prisoner of the Shi'ar Imperial Guard, subject to the mind control of Oracle! Will Captain America be able to rally the troops for this much needed rescue? Plus, Quasar joins the fray when starts trailing the Shi'ar for himself!
description.43: OPERATION: GALACTIC STORM PART 4 Wonder Man finds himself fighting Captain Atlas, but has to wonder why. Captain America relieves Simon of his bodyguard duties, placing him instead in the front line of battle! Teenage musician Rick Jones decides to play nice with Wonder Man after previous disagreements. All this, and the Kree Eternal rises!
description.44: What if the Fantastic Five (including Spider-Man) had invaded the Negative Zone? The Time-Keepers are looking to dissolve certain universes and can the FF dash their plans of using Annihilus and Doom to stop the birth of Franklin Richards? And what is Franklin's role to play in this multiversal struggle?
description.45: OPERATION: GALACTIC STORM PART 3 Quasar alone must defend the tomb of Mar-Vell. It's a full-fledged assault by the Imperial Guard, and Wendell Vaughn may have underestimated Shi'ar strength! Guest-starring Starfox!
description.47: Cardiac may not be as misinformed as Spider-Man believed, after a sinister plot by the TechToy Factory comes to light. A new victim of Carnage emerges. Peter must make a choice between saving one person's life over another.
description.48: Operation Galactic Storm Part 5. As an intergalactic war flares up between the Kree and the Shi'Ar, the Avengers must split into three different groups to attempt to stem the tides of war.
description.49: When Rick Jones has a horrifying dream about the future, he contacts the Avengers for help. But before Captain America can respond, Rick Jones is captured by the Kree Imperial Guard. What did he see? Plus: Who is the Supreme Intelligence?
description.53: Danger stalks the'Rebels'in the form of the massive'World Devastators,'dark side'machines'that destroy everything in their path. Their current target is the'planet'Mon Calamari, which will be destroyed unless'Lando Calrissian'and the Rebel forces can reach it in time. Meanwhile,'Luke'meets the face behind the'Force storm,'a familiar face, while'Leia'feels Luke being torn away.
description.61: Doc teams up to defeat the ghoulish Nightmare!
description.63: The Owl swoops in during Daredevil’s night watch, and all of New York City will tremble.
description.64: Captain Britain confronts the mysterious Roma, and discovers a dark secret about Exclaibur in the process!
description.65: Hulk goes to town on a battalion of SHIELD robots!
description.66: America goes to war! When secret missile silos targeted at Russia are activated, American officials scramble to stop it! Will Iron Man finally don his Iron Man armor MKV III suit to save the day?
description.67: Eric's Christmas preparations are interrupted by Groonk!
description.69: X-Factor's conflict with Ricochet is resolved after his true identity is revealed. The team takes on Mr. Sinister and his Nasty Boys, a gang of mutant followers. What is Sinister's next move? And will X-Factor uncover his motives before it's too late?
description.71: They might finally be home, but there's no rest in sight for Marvel's First Family! A series of mysterious abductions hafve been taking place on Yancy Street, with the victims vanishing without a trace. There's only one man for the job - Yancy Street's very own Ben Grimm, aka the Thing!
description.72: The X-Men have been transported to a mysterious, war-torn land. Separated, they must now regroup and escape...if they can!
description.73: Will a date night with Jean Grey turn into a rendezvous with Mystique in a seedy motel? Not if Spiral can help it!
description.76: Jennifer goes home for the holidays to spend Christmas with her father, who can't get used to his "new daughter". With a little bit of Christmas magic, Jen is able to make her father's wish come true!
description.81: The final battle between the West Coast Avengers and the Night Shift! Earth's Mightiest Heroes seem to have the upper hand until Stannish joins the fight!
description.83: What if What if made the most hilarious comic you've ever read? Led by the Watcher like you've never see before, take a look at the funny underbelly of the Marvel Universe.
description.87: The deeply misguided Cardiac is causing headache for Spider-Man, taking to the streets with a new brand of vigilantism. Will Spider-Man be able to prevent the reckless destruction of the TechToy factory? The return of Cletus Kasady, stirring up trouble on Ryker's Island as only a true thug can!
description.88: The Avengers take on Swordsman and his mysterious accomplice Magdalene. Swordsman withdraws because of a crippling headache, and Magdalene reveals her dimension-warping abilities!
description.89: Cap finds himself in a fight for his life as Jack O' Lantern and Blackwing try to kill him for fun! But when the Scourge appears the truth about the Redskull's death is revealed!

8.text: Baron Strucker makes a power play that leaves Fury and his new agents reeling. The Super Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. vs. the deadly Balance of Terror!

9.text: Darkhawk and Venom’s brawl continues! Darkhawk must triumph against Venom to save Mike Powell from the vile Phillipe Bazin.

13.text: It's guest-stars galore as the Web-Slinging Wonder is joined by Solo, Nova, Deathlok, and the Incredible Hulk to face off against the Sinister Six!

14.text: Northstar as you’ve never known him before!

15.text: The secret history of Team X revealed! Turns out that Omega Red has an old score to settle with Wolverine, Sabretooth and Maverick.  But will Mojo and Fenris stop them all for good?

16.text: The Silver Surfer is infected with a virus that strips him of all his powers! But it's only when the Surfer comes face to face with his dark side that he may be forced into battle.

19.text: With Cannonball dead, X-Force is turned upside down. With the attack triggering a distant memory, Cable travels through time to learn more about his own timeline. What will his discoveries mean for the team?

20.text: The Infinity Watch is gathered and the Infinity Gems are handed out. Drax obtains the Power Gem, Moondragon the Mind Gem, Pip the Space Gem, Gamora the Time Gem, and Adam Warlock gains the Soul Gem.

21.text: Doctor Strange and his team battle and soon defeat Nox and her sons, but could this easy victory be part of a bigger plan?

23.text: Daredevil’s “Nocturnal Hunter” is none other than the Owl! And this night-stalking foe has more power than ever before.

34.text: A weakened and diminished Vulture returns to New York with a death wish for Spider-Man …and Aunt May!

35.text: Darkhawk comes across an unfortunate turn of events as the Caribbean-bound plane that he’s stowed away on crashes on a mysterious island…

36.text: Rancor continues her search for her ancestor Wolverine. Will her band of mutant killers prove too much for the Guardians? Plus, the new Starhawk has teammates wondering if he’s an enemy or ally!

37.text: After Death's Head II absorbs 104 subjects, subject 105...a.k.a. the original Death's Head...comes a callin'.

38.text: The Living Eraser ruins Jen and Wyatt's date night!

39.text: Deathlok the Demolisher is back in town! Deathlok makes a triumphant return to doing what he does best- destroying! Plus, what happens when Deathlok encounters Ghost Rider? Too much violence! Guest-starring the Spirit of Vengeance in “Nightmares of Vengeance”!

41.text: With the Warriors disbanded, Thrasher gets involved with the Folding Circle, Tai drops a bombshell on Silhouette, and Vance fights criminal charges.

50.text: It’s a brand new direction for S.H.I.E.L.D., as Nick Fury recruits a wave of superhero agents! Meet Ivory, Psi-Borg, Knockabout, and Violence!

54.text: The mad Baroness has her hands on the most destructive force in the Marvel Universe: The Cassidy Crystals! Spider-Man must prevent the deployment of a weapon that induces nightmarish terror. Find out why the only thing we have to fear…is fear itself!

56.text: The Hulk arrives to aid the Wallcrawler against the threat of the Sinister Six!

57.text: The Hand's plans for Omega Red have blown up in their face! Their would-be weapon has ditched his mission for an all-out grudge match with Wolverine and his team of X-Men.

58.text: The Silver Surfer is brought head on with the Collection Agency... But they are no match for the infamous Surfer.

59.text: As the battle between X-Force and the Brotherhood continues, the X-Force finds new ways to defeat their foes. Despite the heroes' training and experience, nothing will prepare them for handling the repercussions of the battle.

60.text: After saving the universe from Thanos and ultimately acquiring his prize, the Infinity Gauntlet, Adam Warlock finds himself on trial, judged by the very cosmic beings who supported him in the conflict.

61.text: Doc teams up to defeat the ghoulish Nightmare!

63.text: The Owl swoops in during Daredevil’s night watch, and all of New York City will tremble.

75.text: Rancor’s on the hunt for Wolverine! But it’s the 31st century- can Wolverine possibly be alive? The new Starhawk bursts on the scene!

76.text: Jennifer goes home for the holidays to spend Christmas with her father, who can't get used to his "new daughter". With a little bit of Christmas magic, Jen is able to make her father's wish come true!

78.text: Nick Fury and Alpha Flight’s Weapon Omega team-up to stop Ultimatum from wiping out the World Unity Council. A cruise goes horribly awry, as the world’s peacekeepers fall under attack by a terrorist cell! Plus, Nick Fury goes black-tie!

79.text: Deathlok faces Death! Who will stop at nothing to ensure Deathlok’s permanent end? An explosive conclusion that will leave you reeling!

80.text: Three holiday-themed tales from some of Marvel's top talent. Dan Slott! Louise Simonson! June Brigman! These Marvel legends deliver Christmas cheer with a dash of danger.

83.text: What if "What if" made the most hilarious comic you've ever read? Led by the Watcher like you've never seen him before, take a look at the funny underbelly of the Marvel Universe.

86.text: The New Warriors' investigation into the Taylor Foundation's relationship with the Yakuza takes them to Japan!

91.text: THE HERO KILLERS PART 1.  Spider-Man and the New Warriors team-up to investigate Target Technologies complex, but will they be able to withstand an attack from the powerful Dreadnoughts?

92.text: CITIZEN KANG PART 3 Time and space converge across the continuum, as the Fantastic Four joins the fray against Kang! What is Timely Industries? Plus, a special featurette highlighting the top ten villains of the Fantastic Four!

94.text: CITIZEN KANG PART 4 An Avengers Annual that shines the spotlights on the villains! A rundown of who's fighting who when it comes to Earth's Mightiest, plus PART 4 of the CITIZEN KANG event! Featuring "Boy's Night Out" by Scott Benson, in which the Avenging men try to unwind as though they aren't the planet's protectors.

95.text: In this explosive annual, Hulk teams up with the likes of the Thing, Doctor Strange, and more! And the evil they face is unrelenting!

96.text: CITIZEN KANG PART 2 Featuring the "Ten Most Heinous Enemies of the Mighty Thor"! Think you can guess who made the list? Plus, "Paradise Lost", another time-displaced tale brought to you by Kang the Conqueror.

98.text: CITIZEN KANG PART 1 When the Vision goes missing in Timely, Wisconsin, Captain America investigates. But if Cap's in present-day Wisconsin, why does it feel like the very distant past? Cap and Diamondback discuss their worst villains, and Falcon gets new threads!

99.text: The Brotherhood of Mutants attempt to build their ranks even further through an alliance with the Morlocks. Meanwhile, tensions in X-Force rise as certain member's pasts are called into question.
